Package com.inrupt.client.util

Utility classes for the Inrupt Java Client Libraries.

This module contains a few utility classes used throughout the Inrupt CLient Libraries.

IOUtils helps with working with I/O streams.

URIBuilder helps with building java.net.URI objects.

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IOUtils
    IOUtility methods for use with the Inrupt Java Client Libraries.
    URIBuilder
    A utility for building URI objects.
